column4: Anyone help me solve some issues with a wireless net card under xubuntu?

Prism2, I believe. It's a D-Link SWL-650. It works w/ the orinoco_cs driver... EXCEPT... it generates a lot of TX timeouts, especially when I try to print to remote print server... enough that I can't actually print.
I have two laptops... one does just fine, the other doesn't. Identical setups, except for the cards.
